        "id": "l9-d04",
        "japanese": "いいえ、ギターは あまり じょうずじゃありません。でも、歌が すきです。",
        "speaker": "Noah",
      },
      {
        "english": "Do you understand Japanese songs?",
        "grammarIds": [
          "l9-understand",
        ],
        "id": "l9-d05",
        "japanese": "日本の 歌が わかりますか。",
        "speaker": "Hana",
      },
      {
        "english": "I understand a little, because the words are simple.",
        "grammarIds": [
          "l9-understand",
          "l9-reason",
        ],
        "id": "l9-d06",
        "japanese": "すこし わかります。ことばが やさしいですから。",
        "speaker": "Noah",
      },
      {
        "english": "Would you like to go to a concert together next time?",
        "grammarIds": [],
        "id": "l9-d07",
        "japanese": "こんど、いっしょに コンサートへ 行きませんか。",
        "speaker": "Hana",
      },
      {
        "english": "Definitely! Because I like jazz, I am looking forward to it.",
        "grammarIds": [
          "l9-reason",
          "l9-preference",
        ],
        "id": "l9-d08",
        "japanese": "ぜひ！ ジャズが すきですから、たのしみです。",
        "speaker": "Noah",
      },
    ],
    "exerciseIds": [
